{"tid":1980950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「佛州白癡」登熱搜榜首! 開放海灘千人湧進 當日確診最高紀錄","createTime":"2020-04-20T11:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T11:53:06.000Z","uid":75969,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f01b3ccdd708c7e8198214b4852fbc4fd3a91c3e","tid":1980950,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/395/5e9d69244bc19.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F395%2F5e9d69244bc19.PNG&h=5387aad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國佛羅里達州17日下午5時重新開放部分沙灘和公園，一時之間海灘人數突破百人，而且都沒戴口罩。當日，佛羅里達州當日的新增確診案例單日最高，累計超過2.5萬例，748人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「佛州白癡」（Florida Morons）一詞一度登上美國推特熱搜第一名。有位網友引述事件原始，費城1918年結束西班牙大流感隔離措施，之後舉行遊行慶祝，結果數天後醫院病床全滿。該網友勸佛州要以這件事為前車之鑑。<br />\n<br />\n疫情嚴重的美國佛羅里達州17日開放部分沙灘及公園，關在家許多天的民眾紛紛向海灘湧入，美國民眾大量湧現，慢跑、溜狗、騎自行車等，而且當中許多人沒有戴口罩。當日的確診數突破單日最高紀錄，來到25,492例。此事件一度讓「佛州白癡」一詞登上推特熱搜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-20/394390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-04-20%2F394390&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=7253391a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-20/394390</a>"},{"pid":"908cb77f9ef5c0f0c82453dbeca2ac08c88d015f","tid":1980950,"uid":275058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"Whitt trash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f6a0569a841a73b804406a814c6c6233120eb8","tid":1980950,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"美國咁搞法肯定開始內鬥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}